{"word":"σύμβολον","slug":"σύμβολον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n98312\" key=\"su/mbolon\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σύμβολον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <sense id=\"n98312.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tally</tr_>, i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">each of two halves</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">corresponding pieces</tr_> of an <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀστράγαλος</foreign> or other object, which two <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ξένοι</foreign>, or any two contracting parties, broke between them, each party keeping one piece, in order to have proof of the identity of the presenter of the other, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀποδεικνύντες τὰ ς. ἀπαίτεον τὰ χρήματα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:86\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.86</biblScope></bibl></cit>.<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">β´; ξένοις τε πέμψω σύμβολ᾽, οἳ δράσουσί σ᾽ εὖ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg003.perseus-grc1:613\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">613</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (cf. Sch.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">διαπεπρισμένα ἡμίσε᾽ ἀκριβῶς ὡσπερεὶ τὰ ς</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0458.tlg001:70\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eub.\">Eub.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">70</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\