.\">Pyrrh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg064:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Art.\">Art.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">χρυσοῦν στέφανον ἔλαβον ς. περιέχοντα τῆς ὑμετέρας πρός με εὐσεβείας</quote_> <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Lond.:3:1178:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PLond.\">PLond.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.1178.13</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> <date TEIform=\"date\">(ii A.D.)</date>. </sense> <sense n=\"5\" id=\"n98312.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> identity-<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">token</tr_> given to Athenian dicasts on entering the courts, entitling them to vote, and on presenting which they received another <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ς</itype>., in exchange for which they received their fee, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg011.perseus-grc1:278\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">278</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:210\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.210</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg003.perseus-grc1:65:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">65.2</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg003.perseus-grc1:68:2\" defau